<plot>La Estradense soda factory in Buenos Aires is a beautiful chaos of clanking red crates, blue bottles and conveyor belts crisscrossing the warehouse. In the midst of this is Miguel, who has been repairing soda siphons for 30 years. As the boxes crash around him Miguel ponders on his mortality, and wonders what will happen to all the broken bottles when he's gone.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?176756</url></doc>
